		<h2>Legal Area</h2>
		<div class="list">

			

			
<a class="column-2 selected" href="https://www.armaniexchange.com/us/Help/LegalArea/PrivacyPolicy">Privacy Policy</a>
			
<a class="column-2" href="https://www.armaniexchange.com/us/Help/LegalArea/ReturnPolicy">Return Policy</a>
			
